where state A is the visible species and state B is the invisible dark state. Exchange from states A to B is described by the pseudo-first-order rate constant Ì†µÌ≥Äoapnp, and exchange from states B to A is described by the first-order rate constant off. Thus, at equilibrium:
Ì†µÌ≥Äoapnp A = Ì†µÌ≥Äoff B . (77)

